text: Totallywicked-eliquid.com has the best vapors products from E-cig kits to Fluid, Tanks to Atomizers and everything in between. The fluid is by far the best anywhere, period! If you ever do have a question or a problem there customer service is A+++. They solve problems fast and effectively. They answer any questions or concerns in a very timely manor. They truly care about there customers and it shows. They are saving lives everyday. I have been with them since 2009 and would never even consider another store to do business with!
